---
title: Bavarian Crispy Pork Belly & Braised Cabbage with Apple-Thyme Sauce, Creamy Mash & Gravy
description: Crispy pork belly is a staple in any Bavarian cafe, and we’re ready to be transported! This almighty protein is best enjoyed with an array of classic sides, including creamy potato mash, tangy braised cabbage and a sweet apple and thyme sauce. Dig in!
